{"tid":1564802,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋節 - 月餅起義","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T09:52:18.000Z","uid":235006,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c58ef8c183f62b59e9eec336ce3fb20667172d4","tid":1564802,"uid":235006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經過今次運動之後，你認為中共在多大程度上會禁止民間食月餅、玩燈籠、取消中秋節？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉，吃月餅之所以在民間廣為流傳，還與明朝開國皇帝朱元璋有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n『當時正值元朝末年，中原廣大人民不堪忍受元朝統治階級的殘酷統治，各類反抗活動紛紛湧現。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">豬</span>元璋藉此機會，便聯合各路<span style=\"color: red;\">義士</span>準備起義。<br />\n但朝庭官兵搜查很嚴密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，傳遞消息十分困難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n軍師劉伯溫便想出一計策，到處散佈流言，說有冬瘟流行，除非家家戶戶都在中秋節買月餅來吃，才能避免。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n命令屬下把藏有「八月十五夜起義的紙條藏入餅子中，人們買了月餅回到家中，發覺裏面藏着紙條，上面寫着：「中秋夜，殺韃子，迎義軍!」，再派人分頭傳送到各地起義軍中，通知他們在八月十五日晚同時起義響應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到了起義的那天，各路義軍果然一齊響應，起義軍如星火燎原。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n很快，徐達就攻下元大都，起義大獲成功。明太祖朱元璋月餅起義就這麼流傳至今。』<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfcf34c9636fa2d1d0d04b3d1100f5b1029bbd76","tid":1564802,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97f3aa90b6e3b7640cc8e95d04841a2d8b1f2fe4","tid":1564802,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f375a7133348ab4dc27b24783fc4f152ddfc23a4","tid":1564802,"uid":266735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"煲蠟乃是中秋傳統活動，起義時請不要忘記傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4af91c601507732ca032d6d0d79bbfb7ff65607","tid":1564802,"uid":127753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep